title: Hawkwind 1971 Wolverhampton & Potters Bar (FLAC)
description:
OK folks, here&#039;s the FLAC versions of those 1971 MP3s that were posted on TPB two days ago. 

Together, these shows have previously done the rounds as a bootleg called "Only Dreaming."


NOTE - these are live audience recording and meet Hawkwind&#039;s trading restrictions.

Support the Hawks! - go to their gigs and buy their official stuff :)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Quality around 8. Excellent, by early 70s standards!
